These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, argentine, french, australian
1. the argentine is in an odd position##4
2. the australian is between the brazilian and the argentine##2
3. the australian is on the right of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | brazilian | australian | argentine | french |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, corn, apricot, mango
1. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person eating mango##1
2. the person eating corn is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating corn is on the left or right of the person eating raspberry##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Food   | corn | raspberry | mango | apricot |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, sports, epic, fantasy
1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
2. the person watching action movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching epic movies is between the person watching fantasy movies and the person watching sports movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | action | fantasy | epic | sports |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, sailing, handball, tennis
1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
2. the person who's sport is handball is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is tennis is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person who's sport is handball##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |       3       |   4    |
| Sport   | sailing | parkour | tennis | handball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-5::.
