.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-12::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, ship, helicopter, bus
1. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
2. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
3. the person driving the ship is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |  3  |    4    |
| Transport   | helicopter | ship | bus | airplane |

