.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, soy-milk, sprite, tea
1. the person drinking sprite is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking sprite is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking coffee##2
3. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2     |  3   |   4   |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | sprite | coffee | tea |

