.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, garlic, plum, zucchini
1. the person eating garlic is the person eating garlic##1
2. the person eating zucchini is on the left or right of the person eating plum##3
3. the person eating plum is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating banana is in an even position##4
5. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person eating garlic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food   | plum | zucchini | garlic | banana |

